Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.99,0:22:28.36,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,やめっ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.29,0:22:46.86,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,お願いします
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.10,0:22:50.17,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,まりなを返してください
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.47,0:22:54.60,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,どこの誰だか存じませんが
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.99,0:23:02.46,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,まりなは　おなかを痛めて産んだ　大切な娘なんです
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.32,0:23:06.53,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,まりちゃん　ごめんね
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.53,0:23:08.54,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,いいママじゃなかったよね
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.54,0:23:12.51,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,でも　大好きだからお願い
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.19,0:23:15.79,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,帰ってきて
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.47,0:23:24.84,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,まりなちゃんはしずかちゃんにひどいことをする
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.92,0:23:26.66,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 1,0:23:58.17,0:24:01.88,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,まりなちゃん　ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:24:02.84,0:24:05.88,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,まりなちゃんのパパとママ
Dialogue: 1,0:24:05.88,0:24:08.79,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,まりなちゃんじゃなくてごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:24:09.44,0:24:12.33,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,一緒にいられなくしてごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:24:16.02,0:24:17.66,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,まりなちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:24:19.84,0:24:23.81,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,殺して　ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:24:28.62,0:24:30.15,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,考えなきゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:24:31.58,0:24:35.41,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,ぼくは何をしちゃったのか　どうすればよかったのか
Dialogue: 1,0:24:35.80,0:24:37.00,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚ピー
Dialogue: 1,0:24:37.90,0:24:40.21,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,これからどうすればいいのか
Dialogue: 1,0:24:40.21,0:24:41.37,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚ピー
Dialogue: 1,0:24:46.90,0:24:48.70,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,ありがとう　章魚ピー
Dialogue: 1,0:24:49.77,0:24:51.42,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,殺してくれて
Dialogue: 1,0:24:56.52,0:24:57.80,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,それで
Dialogue: 1,0:24:58.62,0:25:02.76,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,しずかちゃんともう一度　お話ししなきゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:25:09.74,0:25:12.11,JP - down,Staff A,0,0,0,,おーい　こっち何かあるぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:25:12.11,0:25:14.12,JP - down,Staff B,0,0,0,,おいおい　これ何
Dialogue: 1,0:25:14.12,0:25:15.91,JP - down,Staff C,0,0,0,,えっ　何　何
Dialogue: 1,0:25:16.34,0:25:18.99,JP - down,Staff A,0,0,0,,えっ　ヤバくねこれ
Dialogue: 1,0:25:20.33,0:25:21.60,JP - down,Staff A,0,0,0,,子供
Comment: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.63,CN - down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:21.23,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我很擔心你就跟過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:22.14,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:24.02,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:25.97,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,什麼東西 好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:27.95,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:30.80,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,啊 說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.22,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:38.65,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:48.73,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,因為章魚噼的魔法 麻里奈死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:52.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 靜香那不是魔法是快樂道具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:56.82,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,啊 章魚噼是從快樂星球來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.62,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我是快樂星人噼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.86,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,記得 是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.68,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,快樂果實很好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:05.74,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:10.83,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不對 太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:14.71,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:15.51,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:19.56,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,「什麼」奇怪 意義不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:23.88,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,為什麼要殺了她 明明有其它的辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.50,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但是麻里奈她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:28.38,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,而且你為什麼 若無其事地扔下她就走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.47,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,你應該知道會惹出麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:37.05,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,東 東君 感覺你好恐怖噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.55,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,要更加開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:41.56,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,章魚 有「人」可是死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.69,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,你什麼說話方式 搞什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:46.99,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.46,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,你先閉嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.76,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.67,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但是 麻里奈是因為魔法而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.21,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.00,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,魔法什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:04.88,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,先 先不管是魔法還是什麼 殺了人就是殺了人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:09.02,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世 我認為你會進感化院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.38,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:16.40,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,「這是外星人做的」解釋根本行不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.49,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那我就不能去見恰噼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:26.41,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我在書上讀到過 要想減輕罪行只能自首
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.15,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,馬上去警局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.31,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:32.37,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,還有其它的辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.43,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,其它的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.43,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,自首以外的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:38.76,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我不是很懂書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.55,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君你挺了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:47.03,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,在小說裡 有把罪名嫁禍給他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.06,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.77,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不對 那是虛構的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:53.18,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,常見的是把犯罪隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.35,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,算是基本的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:56.19,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.34,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那 就這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:00.55,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:03.02,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:09.13,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我不想進感化院 那就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.67,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那個 要怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:16.40,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,啊 不對 那也是犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.00,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,再說了只靠小孩子如何隱藏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.04,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,有章魚噼的魔法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:27.06,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,所以 東君能不能幫我想個辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.12,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,這種事情我怎麼可能做得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:29.76,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.42,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,為什麼做不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:37.76,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,只有我們兩個的話 肯定很快就會被捉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:41.18,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,所以我希望東君你能幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.99,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我既沒有朋友 也不能依靠媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.19,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,其他人也不能依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.20,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.98,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,哥哥明明就能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.15,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.30,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,除了你之外就沒有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:03.22,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.39,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我的話 能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.12,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,「感化院」是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.01,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,喂 章魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.06,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.49,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,這個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.57,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 那個是「記憶盒子」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.19,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我不是問名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:35.95,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,放進去的東西能夠保持原有的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.83,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,比如說漂亮的葉子之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.46,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,它還能改變大小嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:41.96,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:56.06,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,總之先把雲母坂埋起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.54,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,兇器就藏在章魚的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.24,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:01.39,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,還有就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:05.57,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼 噼 噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.82,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,這樣真的沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:10.74,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼 變身調色盤的偽裝可是很完美的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:12.74,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.57,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那行 我去拿鏟子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.20,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,千萬不要被家裡人懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.77,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,否則 全部功夫都白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:20.63,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:22.86,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.01,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.45,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,這樣真的可以嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:37.09,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 我今後以麻里奈的身份活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:41.04,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,還有把麻里奈藏起來 這些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:42.62,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.60,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:47.50,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你這種說話方式 會暴露啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:53.64,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我會做好的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.59,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你又這麼說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,只要靜香能笑出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我今後會以麻里奈的身份加油努力的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:46.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,像麻里奈一樣活蹦亂跳 我會努力扮演的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.23,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:01.23,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.90,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,結穗是什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.04,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,窗簾 裝窗簾上的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:11.61,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,用別人賺的錢淨買些破爛東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:12.69,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,你個寄生蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.33,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.94,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,那 那經常去夜總會的你算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:18.74,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,那是我 自己辛苦賺的血汗錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.66,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,我愛怎麼花我就怎麼花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.75,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,啊 我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:22.82,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:32.33,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,要是打到眼睛可怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:34.90,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,她是女孩要是在臉上留了疤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:37.22,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,都說了 根本沒受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.46,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,麻里奈也說自己沒事的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:43.90,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,麻里奈還能問你要點醫藥費
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:48.14,CN - down,Mairna's dad,0,0,0,,成天妄想被害 有完沒完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:51.44,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,所以我才受不了你這樣毫不工作的廢物女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.33,CN - up,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,{\an8}好過分…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.65,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈的爸爸和媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:58.15,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,每天說好多話 關係非常好呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.36,CN - up,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,{\an8}我是為了麻里奈和你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.57,CN - up,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,{\an8}為家庭盡心盡責犧牲奉獻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.66,CN - up,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,{\an8}別好像我們欠了你恩情似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.16,CN - up,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,{\an8}你成天哭能解決問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.16,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:04.16,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那麼 我們去找恰噼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.50,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,啊 不錯呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:10.08,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不行的說 都說了現在不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:13.74,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,恰噼在你父親住的地方 那可是東京啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:15.83,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,小孩子自己去太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.38,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:20.85,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我們得等到這隻章魚融進她家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.41,CN - up,Maripi,0,0,0,,噼 噼 噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:25.11,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,說起來「離婚調停」是什麼呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:27.64,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,麻里奈媽媽一直都在說的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.76,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那邊的我已經埋好了應該沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.81,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,但我們應該暫時離開城鎮一段時間避嫌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.19,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,從現在開始仔細制定計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.04,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,執行就放在暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.66,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,在那之前要每天放學後開作戰會議
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.49,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.29,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.32,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.75,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不對不對 我明明沒時間做些事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.03,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,今天得趕緊回家好好學習才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:10:59.92,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.35,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,在外面玩耍挺少見的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:01.89,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.39,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,是班裡的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:07.52,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:10.82,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 還真不叫我「哥哥」了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.49,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,你是東君的哥哥嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.58,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,噼 嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:19.65,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤 潤也才是你回來挺早的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:23.11,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,啊沒有 接下來我要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:26.32,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,媽媽那邊你幫我去哄哄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.55,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:30.89,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:36.37,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤也他 實際上沒有打工的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:39.39,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,多少零用錢他要都能得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:42.16,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,但卻總是讓媽媽她擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.63,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,是 是嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:47.44,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,還擅自用自己賺的錢買了那傻缺的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.35,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,明明只需要好好學習就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:54.82,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,明明比起任何人 都更加備受期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.53,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.44,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.90,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,拿走它不就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:02.40,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.37,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:08.49,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,這樣的話 那個人肯定會因震驚而辭去工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:12.42,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不行 他恐怕是不會這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.67,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,再說了 那可是盜竊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.12,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:20.01,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我認為東君你 能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:32.11,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這裡就是東君的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.67,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,所以 要拿走什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.48,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,笨蛋 閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.79,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,萬一發生意外 有章魚噼的魔法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:40.72,CN - down,Maripi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:45.66,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,雖這麼說 但帶這種傢伙回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:46.32,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,總感覺很開心呢噼 東君 噼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.37,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.07,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤也只有在洗澡的時候才會摘下戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:54.84,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,現在進入他的房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:00.51,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.31,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,太好了呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.86,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,好 只要把它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.31,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,快看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:11.60,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,我終於買到了 和女朋友一對的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:16.05,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,果然這種東西 用自己的錢買才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:19.42,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,他到底在裝什麼正常人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:25.26,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,明明想要的東西 無論什麼都能得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:29.69,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,對了 你用的那個很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:33.69,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,下次等打工錢入帳 我也給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.62,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,被發現了會生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.92,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,喂 你就沒有道具想想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.98,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我不知道噼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:50.92,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,也 也不是那個  噼 也不是這個噼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.09,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.64,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,手機 手機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.64,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,窗戶 我有打開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:13.86,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,差點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:16.22,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,要被發現就慘了 快逃 章魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:19.16,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 東君 來這裡噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.01,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:27.17,CN - down,Announcement,0,0,0,,重量超過 重量超過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.25,CN - down,Announcement,0,0,0,,電池沒電了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:29.89,CN - up,Azuma,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:36.80,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.42,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,我記得聽到了什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:41.95,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,是錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.41,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 噼 噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.34,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:49.66,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:52.04,CN - down,Announcement,0,0,0,,重量超過 重量超過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:50.83,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.75,CN - up,Azuma,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.96,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.87,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 噼 噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.14,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:07.97,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,你沒事嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:16.53,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.68,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,有沒有哪裡會痛呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.69,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.11,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這樣啊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:23.93,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.56,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,太好了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:36.12,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 但是 戒指沒有拿走呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:38.22,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:39.20,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:42.13,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,那麼 需要懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:44.59,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,鬆餅點心就不給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.04,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:49.05,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,你哥哥一直都是滿分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.47,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,你可以忍耐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.05,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.41,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那就 下次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.55,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,下次的我 會更加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:03.66,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,啊啊 又沒得吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:06.39,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,難得我今天給你做了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:10.63,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,對不起 今天我會忍耐的 下次肯定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.06,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,總感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:15.16,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,這些努力全都沒什麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.36,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,不管你做什麼 都還是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:20.53,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.51,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:30.69,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,請不要 對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:43.57,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你們兩人怎麼了 破爛不堪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,很破破爛爛嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.36,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:26.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,上次在東君家 發現了一個糟糕的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:27.44,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:31.23,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,拍拍翅膀承受不了人類的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:35.30,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,所以沒辦法飛到恰噼所在的東京噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:39.43,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,無所謂 我從來沒有期待過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.02,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.68,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那麼 只有船和新幹線了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.39,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.32,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,剩下的 就只是錢的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.19,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:52.72,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,吶 為什麼快樂道具這麼沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:53.53,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:56.66,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,就這水準還來地球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.87,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,才沒有這回事噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:02.73,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,在快樂星球上有更多的快樂道具噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.59,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,像是土星狗立體模型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:05.82,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,樂色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.04,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,還有「大快樂時鐘」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:12.88,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,這個可是隨時都能穿越時空的好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:14.75,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那現在趕緊把它拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.21,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,全部都修改為一切沒發生不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:20.26,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 這是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.58,CN - up,Azuma,0,0,0,,你這
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:24.05,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,因為 我現在回不了快樂星球噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.44,CN - up,Shizuka,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:28.94,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世 我們去東京搭乘新幹線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:32.08,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯 那就 來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:32.75,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:38.22,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,三人在一起的時候很快樂呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:41.16,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香能夠快樂笑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.78,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,真希望 能一直這樣生活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞 但是 說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:52.25,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,為什麼我不能回去快樂星球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:58.04,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,到最後你連咱媽的六十歲壽宴都沒露面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:57.52,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,嗯 完全沒頭緒噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:01.28,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,那是因為我也有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.60,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,就只是賺不了錢的家庭主婦教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:04.85,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.98,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,總是去夜總會有家也不回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:09.93,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,那我用自己賺的錢去喝酒什麼不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:13.94,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,你對自家人的親戚就這冷漠態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.39,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,是吧 麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.89,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,唔 什麼呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:21.52,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,麻里 你又這樣說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.94,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,是學校現在流行的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.83,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,麻里奈最近變得開朗起來挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:29.60,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,反觀你媽 還是嘮嘮叨叨的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:35.39,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,麻里奈 你要不來爸爸這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:36.16,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:39.83,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,撫養權不是已經談妥了嗎 明明你根本不想養她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.11,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,爸爸那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:40.72,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:44.43,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那是不是東京 是恰噼在的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.13,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我要去噼 爸爸那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:51.02,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,哦 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:54.79,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,那麼 麻里奈也來爸爸這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:55.57,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.91,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊 你要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.41,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.83,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.49,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,今天爸爸不回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:10.90,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.28,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:13.15,CN - up,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,你那種說話方式怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:14.04,CN - down,Takopoi,0,0,0,,得告訴東君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.12,CN - down,Takopoi,0,0,0,,暑假前就能去了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.04,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:20.47,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,太好啦噼 這樣子靜香她也會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:21.48,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:22.17,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:24.52,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,怎麼了噼媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:25.51,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,說話方式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.27,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,啊 是啊噼 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.85,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我得注意點噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.72,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,畢竟今後 我要以麻里奈的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:41.99,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,說話沒大沒小 改
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:43.93,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:46.77,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,對不起 噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:50.65,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:51.58,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.54,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.53,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,你懂得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:57.37,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:21:59.66,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:01.50,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我 不敢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.18,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,麻里真的變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:05.97,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,以前一直都站在媽媽這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:08.66,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,明明是個好孩子 聽媽媽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:12.68,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,以 以前 那我改 改成之前的麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:13.18,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:14.31,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:15.89,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:17.64,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,這一切都錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:21.33,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,就算那個男人不懂 什麼也沒察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:21.15,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,媽媽 恐怖 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:22.98,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,但我自明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:25.25,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,這女孩根本不是麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:26.99,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:26.99,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:28.36,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.29,0:22:46.86,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:50.17,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,請把麻里奈還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:54.60,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,我不知道你什麼來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:23:02.46,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,但只有麻里奈 是我最為心疼的親骨肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:06.53,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,麻里 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:08.54,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,我沒能成為一個稱職的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:12.51,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,但是 我一直會愛著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.19,0:23:15.79,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,請你回來好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:24.84,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈對靜香做了很過分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:26.66,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.17,0:24:01.88,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,麻里奈 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:05.88,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,麻里奈的爸爸和媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:08.79,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我不是真正的麻里奈 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.44,0:24:12.33,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我無法讓你們團圓 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:17.66,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.84,0:24:23.81,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我殺了你 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.62,0:24:30.15,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我要思考
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.58,0:24:35.41,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我到底做了什麼 要怎麼做才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.80,0:24:37.00,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.90,0:24:40.21,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,接下來該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.21,0:24:41.37,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.90,0:24:48.70,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,謝謝你 章魚噼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.77,0:24:51.42,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.52,0:24:57.80,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.62,0:25:02.76,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我想和靜香 再一次好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.74,0:25:12.11,CN - down,Staff A,0,0,0,,喂 這裡有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.11,0:25:14.12,CN - down,Staff B,0,0,0,,喂喂 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.12,0:25:15.91,CN - down,Staff C,0,0,0,,欸 什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.34,0:25:18.99,CN - down,Staff A,0,0,0,,欸 這可慘了啊
